5000|$|There {{are several}} {{companies}} producing whisky in Japan, {{but the two}} best-known and most widely available are Suntory and Nikka. Both of these produce blended as well as single <b>malt</b> <b>whiskies</b> and blended <b>malt</b> <b>whiskies,</b> with their main blended whiskies being Suntory [...] (square bottle), and Black Nikka Clear. There are also {{a large number of}} special bottlings and limited editions.|$|R
